Symbol.Script_3D:
if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_OFF then end if not(gs_shadow) then SHADOW OFF
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Styles ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
pen gs_cont_pen gosub iPaneStyle
end
! ============================================================================= ! SUBRUTINES ! ! =============================================================================
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Glass Pane Simple ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
1:
material gs_frame_mat
addy b rotx 90 for i=1 to 2 prism_ 5,tFrame, 0, 0, 15, 0, zzyzx, 15, wFrame, zzyzx-wFrame, 15, wFrame, wFrame, 15, 0, 0, -1 base vert 0, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body -1 addx a mulx -1 next i del 4
for i=1 to 2 prism_ 5, tFrame, 0, 0, 15, a, 0, 15, a-wFrame, wFrame, 15, wFrame, wFrame, 15, 0, 0, -1 addy zzyzx muly -1 next i del 4
if gs_glass_mat=0 then end body -1 material gs_glass_mat
add wFrame, wFrame, (tFrame-tGlass)/2 block a-2*wFrame, zzyzx-2*wFrame, tGlass body -1
del 3
return
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Glass Pane Sliding ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
2: ho = zzyzx bm = (a - 4 * wFrame)/3 + 2*wFrame
addy b rotx 90
material gs_frame_mat
for i=1 to 3 for k=1 to 2 prism_ 5, tFrame, 0, 0, 15, 0, zzyzx, 15, wFrame, zzyzx-wFrame, 15, wFrame, wFrame, 15, 0,0,-1 base vert 0, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body -1 addx bm mulx -1 next k del 4
for k=1 to 2 prism_ 5, tFrame, 0, 0, 15, bm, 0, 15, bm-wFrame, wFrame, 15, wFrame, wFrame, 15, 0,0,-1 base vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 0, 1 vert 0, 1, 0 coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4 body -1 addy zzyzx muly -1 next k del 4
addx bm - wFrame addz tFrame + tGap next i
if gs_glass_mat = 0 then end body -1 material gs_glass_mat
del 7
rotx 90 add wFrame, wFrame, 0
for i=1 to 3 step 1 block bm-2*wFrame, ho-2*wFrame, tFrame addx bm - wFrame addz tFrame + tGap next i
body -1 del 9
return
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iPaneStyle PANESTYLE_SIMPLE = 1 PANESTYLE_SLIDING = 2
dim stStyles[2] stStyles[1] = `Simple` stStyles[2] = `Sliding`
! const values for parameter: iDetlevel3D DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED = 1 DETLEVEL3D_OFF = 2
dim typRes[2] typRes[1] = `Detailed` typRes[2] = `Off`
tGap = 0.003
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types_BA_WMCC" parameters all
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Styles ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
values{2} "iPaneStyle" PANESTYLE_SIMPLE, stStyles[1], PANESTYLE_SLIDING, stStyles[2]
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! 3D detlevel ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
values{2} "iDetlevel3D" DETLEVEL3D_DETAILED, typRes[1], DETLEVEL3D_OFF, typRes[2] ! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Default Sizes ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
values "a" range [2*wFrame,) values "b" range [0.003,) values "zzyzx" range [2*wFrame,) values "tGlass" range (0, tFrame) values "tFrame" range [0.003,) values "wFrame" range (0,)
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "tFrame" then b = tFrame parameters b= b else tFrame = b parameters tFrame = tFrame endif
if iPaneStyle = 2 then if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "tFrame" then b = 3 * tFrame + 2 * tGap parameters b = b else tFrame = (b - 2 * tGap) / 3 parameters tFrame = tFrame endif else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "tFrame" then b = tFrame parameters b = b else tFrame = b parameters tFrame = tFrame endif endif
! ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! Limitations ! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_cont_pen = 0 then parameters gs_cont_pen = 7 if gs_fill_pen = 0 then parameters gs_cont_pen = 91
if iDetlevel3D = DETLEVEL3D_OFF then hideparameter "gs_shadow"
if iPaneStyle = 2 then hideparameter "tGlass"
Symbol.Script_UI:
ui_dialog `Glass Pane Type`
ui_infield{3} "iPaneStyle", 0, 5, 444, 260, 1, 1, 2, 1, 132, 162, 128, 128, 1, stStyles[1], 1, 2, stStyles[2], 2
Symbol.Comment: Simple and sliding glass partition wall pane.
